  <description><![CDATA[<p>This large, impressive hotel boasts a full range of leisure and entertainment facilities. A famous hotel within Italy this is the ideal place to enjoy local Italian atmosphere and hospitality on a grand scale. Traditional in décor with pleasant public rooms to relax in and the optional entertainments programme means there is always something to do each evening. Situated in the centre of the resort, just a short 2 minutes’ walk (150m) from the main village ski lifts.</p>]]></description>
